This yields 0 instead of 3 with no warning:
```scala
def makeF(i: Int) = () => i

trait Foo { val x: Int; val f = makeF(x) }

val bar = new Foo { val x = 3 }

println( bar.f() )
```

This is ok though:
```scala
trait Foo { val x: Int; val f = () => x }

val bar = new Foo { val x = 3 }

println( bar.f() )
```

Thanks!
